# Quotation I like
This too shall pass

# Food or flavour I don‘t like
Hawaiian Pizza - Pineapple in pizza

# A recommendation for something and why: book, TV show, film, place to visit in the world (or in Salzburg)
A book: The picture of Dorian Gray - Oscar Wilde (A satirical portrayal of vanity-driven human degradation).
A film: Mr. Nobody - Jaco Van Dormael (A surreal critique of fate, choice and the illusion of free will).
A place to visit: Colombia (Simply because everyone should experience visiting Colombia at least once in their lifetime.)

# One German language word I have learned and I think is useful for others to know
lüften (it means taking fresh air)
